Create a web application with the following features:

1. User Authentication
   - Login page with email and password
   - Registration page for new users
   - User profile page showing user details
   - Secure password hashing and JWT token-based authentication

2. Task Management
   - Dashboard showing user's tasks
   - Create new task with title, description, due date, and priority
   - Edit existing tasks
   - Delete tasks
   - Mark tasks as complete/incomplete
   - Filter tasks by status and priority

3. User Settings
   - Update profile information
   - Change password
   - Email notification preferences
   - Theme preferences (light/dark mode)

Technical Requirements:
- Modern, responsive UI using Next.js and Tailwind CSS
- RESTful API using FastAPI
- SQLite database with SQLAlchemy ORM
- Secure authentication using JWT tokens
- Form validation using Pydantic
- Real-time updates for task status changes 
